{"id":15432,"date":"2025-10-15T11:43:15","date_gmt":"2025-10-15T11:43:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/?p=15432"},"modified":"2026-01-13T09:04:48","modified_gmt":"2026-01-13T09:04:48","slug":"mr-sami-abu-ahmad-non-executive-un-ddhu-ambassador-mining-gold-sector","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/mr-sami-abu-ahmad-non-executive-un-ddhu-ambassador-mining-gold-sector\/","title":{"rendered":"Mr. Sami Abu Ahmad Appointed Non-Executive UN DDHU Ambassador for the Mining &amp; Gold Sector"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"15432\" class=\"elementor elementor-15432\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9ae9e93 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"56179\" data-id=\"9ae9e93\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-dac6cb7\" data-eae-slider=\"72530\" data-id=\"dac6cb7\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d318b0c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d318b0c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.22.0 - 24-06-2024 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>We are immensely proud to announce that on 15<sup>th<\/sup> May 2025, <a href=\"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/message-from-the-chairman\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mr. Sami Abu Ahmad<\/a>, Chairman of Sam Precious Metals, was officially appointed to serve in a non-executive capacity as <strong>Ambassador for the Mining and Gold Sector<\/strong> for the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.un.org\/en\/about-us\/universal-declaration-of-human-rights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Universal Declaration of Humankind Rights<\/a> <strong>(DDHU)<\/strong> and was invited to attend and speak at the 10th Anniversary Conference of the UN DDHU in Geneva. His address emphasized the urgent need for global collaboration in <a href=\"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/responsible-sourcing-of-gold-and-silver\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">responsible sourcing<\/a>, mercury-free extraction, and the empowerment of <a href=\"https:\/\/sampreciousmetals.com\/custom-minting-services\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mining<\/a> communities.<\/p><p>The title recognizes Mr. Sami\u2019s long-standing commitment to human rights, ethical sourcing, and sustainability across the global precious metals industry. It also reinforces Sam Precious Metals\u2019 role in advocating for transparency, sustainability, and fair economic inclusion, especially in regions where gold production intersects with complex humanitarian challenges.<\/p><p>As Ambassador, Mr. Sami will contribute to international dialogue on the future of utilizing clean mining technologies, representing the values of responsible development and global cooperation.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3002129 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"35850\" data-id=\"3002129\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-86408a9\" data-eae-slider=\"82680\" data-id=\"86408a9\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e9c411 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3e9c411\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.22.0 - 24-06-2024 *\/\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}<\/style><h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">M. Sami Abu Ahmad nomm\u00e9 Ambassadeur non ex\u00e9cutif de l\u2019ONU pour le secteur minier et aurif\u00e8re<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-e9c8fc4 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"32559\" data-id=\"e9c8fc4\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5d37f44\" data-eae-slider=\"92864\" data-id=\"5d37f44\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a71913 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2a71913\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Nous sommes extr\u00eamement fiers d\u2019annoncer que le 15 mai 2025, M. Sami Abu Ahmad, Pr\u00e9sident de Sam Precious Metals, a \u00e9t\u00e9 officiellement nomm\u00e9 pour exercer, \u00e0 titre non ex\u00e9cutif, les fonctions <strong>d\u2019Ambassadeur pour le secteur minier et aurif\u00e8re<\/strong> dans le cadre de la D\u00e9claration Universelle des Droits de l\u2019Humanit\u00e9 <strong>(DDHU)<\/strong> et a \u00e9t\u00e9 invit\u00e9 \u00e0 assister et \u00e0 prendre la parole lors de la Conf\u00e9rence du 10e anniversaire de la DDHU de l\u2019ONU \u00e0 Gen\u00e8ve.<\/p><p>Son discours a soulign\u00e9 l\u2019urgence d\u2019une collaboration mondiale pour un approvisionnement responsable, une extraction sans mercure et l\u2019autonomisation des communaut\u00e9s mini\u00e8res.<\/p><p>Ce titre vient r\u00e9compenser l\u2019engagement de longue date de M. Sami en faveur des droits humains, de l\u2019approvisionnement \u00e9thique et du d\u00e9veloppement durable dans l\u2019industrie mondiale des m\u00e9taux pr\u00e9cieux. Il renforce \u00e9galement le r\u00f4le de Sam Precious Metals dans la promotion de la transparence, de la durabilit\u00e9 et de l\u2019inclusion \u00e9conomique \u00e9quitable, en particulier dans les r\u00e9gions o\u00f9 la production d\u2019or est confront\u00e9e \u00e0 des enjeux humanitaires complexes.<\/p><p>En tant qu&#8217;Ambassadeur, M. Sami contribuera au dialogue international sur l&#8217;avenir de l&#8217;utilisation des technologies mini\u00e8res propres, en repr\u00e9sentant les valeurs de d\u00e9veloppement responsable et de coop\u00e9ration mondiale.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2cfd4a0 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"19746\" data-id=\"2cfd4a0\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-299d077\" data-eae-slider=\"27937\" data-id=\"299d077\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cccc179 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cccc179\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">\u062a\u0639\u064a\u064a\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064a\u062f \u0633\u0627\u0645\u064a \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0623\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0633\u0641\u064a\u0631\u064b\u0627 \u063a\u064a\u0631 \u062a\u0646\u0641\u064a\u0630\u064a \u0644\u0644\u0623\u0645\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062a\u062d\u062f\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0637\u0627\u0639 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0639\u062f\u064a\u0646 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0630\u0647\u0628<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-be7c452 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-eae-slider=\"19967\" data-id=\"be7c452\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"has_eae_slider elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-af05b8e\" data-eae-slider=\"48686\" data-id=\"af05b8e\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4fbc16b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4fbc16b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ar-rtl\" dir=\"rtl\" lang=\"ar\">\n<p>\u0641\u062e\u0631 \u0628\u0627\u0644\u0625\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0646 \u0623\u0646\u0647 \u0641\u064a 15 \u0645\u0627\u064a\u0648 2025\u060c \u062a\u0645 \u062a\u0639\u064a\u064a\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064a\u062f \u0633\u0627\u0645\u064a \u0623\u0628\u0648 \u0623\u062d\u0645\u062f\u060c \u0631\u0626\u064a\u0633 \u0645\u062c\u0644\u0633 \u0625\u062f\u0627\u0631\u0629 \u0634\u0631\u0643\u0629 \u0633\u0627\u0645 \u0644\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u062f\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0645\u064a\u0646\u0629\u060c \u0631\u0633\u0645\u064a\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u064a\u0634\u063a\u0644 \u0645\u0646\u0635\u0628 <strong>\u0633\u0641\u064a\u0631 \u063a\u064a\u0631 \u062a\u0646\u0641\u064a\u0630\u064a<\/strong>\u00a0\u0644\u0642\u0637\u0627\u0639 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0639\u062f\u064a\u0646 \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0630\u0647\u0628 \u0636\u0645\u0646\u00a0<strong>\u0625\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0646 \u062d\u0642\u0648\u0642 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0646\u0633\u0627\u0646\u064a\u0629\u00a0 <\/strong><strong>(DDHU)<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u0648\u0642\u062f \u062f\u064f\u0639\u064a \u0644\u062d\u0636\u0648\u0631 \u0648\u0625\u0644\u0642\u0627\u0621 \u0643\u0644\u0645\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0624\u062a\u0645\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0648\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0634\u0631 \u0644\u0625\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0646 \u062d\u0642\u0648\u0642 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0646\u0633\u0627\u0646\u064a\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0627\u0628\u0639 \u0644\u0644\u0623\u0645\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062a\u062d\u062f\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u062c\u0646\u064a\u0641.<\/p>\n<p>\u0648\u0642\u062f \u0631\u0643\u0651\u0632 \u0641\u064a \u0643\u0644\u0645\u062a\u0647 \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0627\u062c\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u062d\u0629 \u0644\u0644\u062a\u0639\u0627\u0648\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0644\u0645\u064a \u0641\u064a \u0645\u062c\u0627\u0644\u0627\u062a \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0648\u0631\u064a\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0633\u0624\u0648\u0644\u060c \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062a\u0639\u062f\u064a\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0627\u0644\u064a \u0645\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0626\u0628\u0642\u060c \u0648\u062a\u0645\u0643\u064a\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062c\u062a\u0645\u0639\u0627\u062a \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0627\u0645\u0644\u0629 \u0641\u064a \u0642\u0637\u0627\u0639 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0639\u062f\u064a\u0646.<\/p>\n<p>\u064a\u0623\u062a\u064a \u0647\u0630\u0627 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0642\u0628 \u062a\u0642\u062f\u064a\u0631\u064b\u0627 \u0644\u0627\u0644\u062a\u0632\u0627\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u064a\u062f \u0633\u0627\u0645\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0648\u064a\u0644 \u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0641\u0627\u0639 \u0639\u0646 \u062d\u0642\u0648\u0642 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0646\u0633\u0627\u0646\u060c \u0648\u0627\u0644\u062a\u0648\u0631\u064a\u062f \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062e\u0644\u0627\u0642\u064a\u060c \u0648\u0627\u0